metadata.name: I Understand Evil Now
metadata.description:
“You will pay for what you did…to me.”

“I Understand Evil Now” is an artwork made by me, aka Kooshie which portrays anger, depression and guilt in a dark yet colorful way.

- “ ” -

The winner of this piece will receive a free commission by me in this same art-style , As for all the bidders, you will receive a special stamp which will be given out as soon as auction ends!
